Habbatussauda is one of the traditional or herbal medicine existed since a long time ago and this is one of the drugs that was recommended by the Prophet Muhammad. Habbatussaudaâ€™s benefits has been studied extensively in the field of health, habbatussauda also has been widely used to cure various diseases although it takes a long time. One of the benefit is to cure diabetes mellitus. This research will analyze the mathematics models of diabetes using three variables which are glucose, insulin and insulin generalization. Then it will look for the differences before and after consuming habbatussauda by using the mathematics model.